How to use pre-built layouts?

Please do the below change in the html element at templates/element/main.php file. ex: <html data-layout-width="fluid">

Color Scheme:
data-layout-mode="light"
data-layout-mode="dark"
Card Layout:
data-card-layout="borderless"
data-card-layout="border"
Layout Width:
data-layout-width="fluid"
data-layout-width="boxed"
Layout Position:
data-layout-position="fixed"
data-layout-position="scrollable"
Topbar Colors:
data-topbar="light"
data-topbar="dark"
Preloader Option:
data-preloader="disable"
data-preloader="enable"
